Energy-efficient living


2017 Partner of the Year – Sustained Excellence Award
Over 16,000 organizations strive to be named ENERGY STAR® Partner of the Year. And we've done it again. It’s our fourth consecutive year to be honored with the EPA top award for homebuilding: Sustained Excellence. That’s another year of refusing to settle. And a long-standing record of Life. Built. Better.®
Read More



30th Anniversary





30th Anniversary
For generations, Meritage has been bringing families home. Styles have changed over the years, but our commitment to building affordable, energy-efficient homes has not. Meritage was named 2015 ENERGY STAR® Partner of the Year, Sustained Excellence. What does 30 years of excellence look like? Visit any of our communities to see the difference.
Home and community information is subject to change, and homes to prior sale, at any time without notice or obligation. Not an offer or solicitation to sell real property. Offers to sell real property may only be made and accepted at the sales center for individual Meritage Homes communities. See sales associate for details. Meritage Homes® is a registered trademark of Meritage Homes Corporation. ©2015 Meritage Homes Corporation. All rights reserved.




Giving Back to Those that Give So Much


Announcing This Year's Home Recipients
We’re thrilled to announce our 2016 Operation Homefront recipients. Welcome to the Meritage family, U.S. Army Staff Sergeant Joseph Moncrief and U.S. Army Sergeant Jonathan Acuna. Thank you for your service!
